  <summary date="2016-07-27T13:19:55Z" status="Introduced in House">Diesel Emissions Reduction Act of 2016 

This bill amends the Energy Policy Act of 2005 to reauthorize through FY2021 a diesel emissions reduction program. The program authorizes the Environmental Protection Agency to provide grants, rebates, or loans for reducing diesel emissions from certain diesel vehicles or fleets by retrofitting or replacing their engines.</summary>
